<L>__{interior the lifeboat, under the tarp continuous}
<A>__{thunder, rain and surf hammer the tarp from above; pi pulls himself under the tarp. richard parker's grunts and labored breathing can be heard, but man and beast are only fully visible when lightning strikes, pi trying to stay as far away from the tiger as he can manage. before long the boat is tossing pi and the tiger as though in a washing machine, the two helplessly colliding with one another, pi choking as water splashes in.}
